<item>
            <title>[PIG-3292] Logical plan invalid state: duplicate uid in schema during self-join to get cross product</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3292</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi.&lt;br/&gt;
Looks like &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3020&quot; title=&quot;&amp;quot;Duplicate uid in schema&amp;quot; error when joining two relations derived from the same load statement&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3020&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3020&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
but works in a different way.&lt;br/&gt;
Our pig version is: &lt;br/&gt;
Apache Pig version 0.10.0-cdh4.2.0 (rexported) &lt;br/&gt;
compiled Feb 15 2013, 12:20:54&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Accoring to release note, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3020&quot; title=&quot;&amp;quot;Duplicate uid in schema&amp;quot; error when joining two relations derived from the same load statement&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3020&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3020&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is included into CDH 4.2 dist&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://archive.cloudera.com/cdh4/cdh/4/pig-0.10.0-cdh4.2.0.CHANGES.txt&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://archive.cloudera.com/cdh4/cdh/4/pig-0.10.0-cdh4.2.0.CHANGES.txt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem:&lt;br/&gt;
We want to do self join to get cross-product&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
a = load &apos;/input&apos; as (key, x);

a_group = group a by key;
b = foreach a_group {
  y = a.x;
  pair = cross a.x, y;
  generate flatten(pair);
}

dump b;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And an error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
ERROR org.apache.pig.tools.grunt.Grunt - ERROR 2270: Logical plan invalid state: duplicate uid in schema : 1-7::x#16:bytearray,y::x#16:bytearray
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is workaround &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
a = load &apos;/input&apos; as (key, x:&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;);

a_group = group a by key;
b = foreach a_group {
  y = foreach a generate -(-x);
  pair = cross a.x, y;
  generate flatten(pair);
}

dump b;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;CDH 4.2&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
